{"tid":461392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[FAKE NEWS] 特朗普餵魚欠耐性？","createTime":"2017-11-07T13:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T14:25:15.000Z","uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2da7483bae50c79eb91e477a86bf0a815584da58","tid":461392,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"求驗傳媒<br />\n <br />\n一日最衰特朗普？<br />\n<br />\n有圖不代表真相，即使報章報道，也要小心中伏。<br />\n<br />\n星島日報/頭條日報的一篇題為「特朗普餵魚欠耐性 惹網民熱議」的報道，看標題已經知道主角是特朗普，部分內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n「特朗普起初與日本首相安倍晉三一樣，用小杓子將飼料灑入錦鯉池中。但過沒多久，特朗普似乎失去耐心，索性將整個木盒倒過來，把所有飼料倒進魚池。」<br />\n<br />\n看到上面的描述，在看看左圖，特朗普馬上被安倍晉三相比下去。<br />\n<br />\n其實，首先把所有飼料倒進魚池的是安倍晉三（右圖），當時特朗普還拿著小杓子。<br />\n<br />\n當時片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yAaFzb0sG3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyAaFzb0sG3s&d=dM30yAcC%2B%2F4wfHYmLqsYTNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a982c665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yAaFzb0sG3s</a><br />\n<br />\n當然，這樣餵魚是抵鬧的，但總不能全部都入特朗普數，要鬧就兩個都鬧，否則就是選擇性報道。<br />\n<br />\nShare過的，自己識做。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/23376658_1489719774437566_8047017044314458813_n.jpg?oh=0fee2db7c6de9661383e10aac4a1d45a&amp;oe=5A703690\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F23376658_1489719774437566_8047017044314458813_n.jpg%3Foh%3D0fee2db7c6de9661383e10aac4a1d45a%26oe%3D5A703690&h=92495e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/photos/a.693958160680402.1073741828.692298914179660/1489719774437566/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkauyim%2Fphotos%2Fa.693958160680402.1073741828.692298914179660%2F1489719774437566%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=dM30yAcC%2B%2F4wfHYmLqsYTNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=9a59cf53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/photos/a.693958160680402.1073741828.692298914179660/1489719774437566/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"de6283b74243737cf097176753acb85cb4a10f3c","tid":461392,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76204a564e1d65635644493fd7caca1a68d4c23","tid":461392,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"傳媒真係信一成都死"},{"pid":"af93fcfc2784d0e70000c09d5a7191966e2a9b55","tid":461392,"uid":49955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"侵仔倒得串好多喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}